## traceId 传递

```typescript
// ✅ 中间件注入 context，逐层传递
export function createContext(req: Request): Context {
  const traceId = req.headers['x-trace-id'] ?? generateTraceId();
  return { traceId, user: resolveUser(req), logger: logger.child({ traceId }) };
}

// Service / Adapter 接收 traceId，不重新生成
await vectorSearch.search(collection, vector, { traceId: ctx.traceId });
```

- GraphQL context 携带 `traceId`
- 异步任务（队列、定时）继承来源 traceId 或建立 parentSpan
- 前端可选传 `x-trace-id`，便于端到端关联

