## Langfuse 埋点

```typescript
// ✅ AI 调用包裹 trace span
const trace = langfuse.trace({ id: traceId, userId: user.id, name: 'report.generate' });
const generation = trace.generation({
  name: 'sql-generation',
  model: config.modelName,
  input: sanitizePrompt(input.prompt), // 脱敏后
});

try {
  const output = await chain.invoke(input);
  generation.end({ output: summarizeOutput(output), usage: output.usage });
  return output;
} catch (err) {
  generation.end({ level: 'ERROR', statusMessage: err.message });
  logger.error('langchain.invoke.failed', { traceId, model: config.modelName, err });
  throw err;
}
```

- 记录 model 名、token 用量、latency；不记录 API Key
- Prompt 含 PII 时使用 `sanitizePrompt` 或 hash 摘要
- 业务日志 `traceId` 与 Langfuse trace id 对齐

---

## 性能指标

```typescript
// ✅ 关键路径计时
const timer = metrics.startTimer('report.generate.duration');
try {
  // ...
  metrics.increment('report.generate.success');
} catch {
  metrics.increment('report.generate.failure');
  throw;
} finally {
  timer.end();
}
```

- 指标命名与日志 `operation` 保持一致
- 外部依赖分别计量：`qdrant.search.duration`、`redis.get.duration`
- 不在热路径做同步磁盘 IO 写日志

